Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.94,0:00:05.73,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.61,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I always thought he'd committed suicide.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He wasn't such a coward.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.53,0:00:17.49,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He was a guy who'd just grit his teeth and do\Nthe best he could when faced with adversity.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.62,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You'd never hear him complaining.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.96,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.37,0:00:26.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Even when everyone was asleep,\Nhe'd be up drawing something.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.63,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Moritaka, have you read "Star of the Giants?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.59,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then you know that one line of Ryoma Sakamoto's?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.60,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You always did love "Ashita no Joe."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.43,0:00:42.98,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.40,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Dad, I think I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.06,0:00:48.23,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.65,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.61,Default,Boys,0,0,0,,Azuki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.82,0:00:57.62,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's her mom! This has to be Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.03,0:01:04.37,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'll cheer you on from the sidelines while you\Nwork on becoming excellent mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.29,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.33,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.21,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.21,0:01:12.30,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It isn't just you, it's us!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.76,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'll definitely make this dream a reality!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.68,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If I can't do this—
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I won't be a real man!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.14,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm not a man yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.22,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow—
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.23,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,No today,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.27,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm gonna work on my own manga drawing style.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.86,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm gonna work hard on names!
