Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.64,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,Most pros use the G-pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.97,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,The control G-pens give over the intensity \Nof the line really increases the quality.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.81,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,I never got used to it, so I use a Kabura pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.69,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,This type of pen just makes the\Ncut for the purposes of gag manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.56,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,But real pros should use G-pens.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.03,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,I try to use one sometimes, but it's really difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.71,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.17,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Mashiro, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.38,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.38,Default-Italic,Saiko,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.26,0:04:05.01,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,It's great that you're studying hard,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.26,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,but your effort's wasted if you fall\Nasleep in the middle of the test.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.22,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I—I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.19,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Finally done for the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.27,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.53,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone pass out\Nin the middle of a test before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.65,0:04:21.86,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Did you really pass out from studying too hard?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.32,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.66,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,Whatever, it's over and done\Nwith. Wanna hit the movies?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's see something x-rated!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,X-rated?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Sorry, I've got stuff to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.59,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,What's up with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Those two have been inseparable lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.38,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Were you up all night practicing drawing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.26,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was at the studio past midnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Then I went home and practiced\Ntill it was time for school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.10,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If I didn't lose my drawing\Nstreak on the way to school,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.23,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I might've taken the test with this pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.56,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Wow, you even brought it with you and everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.69,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If I can't get used to using this, it's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.57,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There aren't any boundaries in manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.45,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Boundaries?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.45,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Unlike tests, there isn't one way to do manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.91,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Stories and pictures don't\Nhave right or wrong answers.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.08,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm gonna head over to the studio\Nnow, you wanna come along?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.17,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You seem pumped.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.88,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Here you go. Your own key to the studio.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.30,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Y—You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.14,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's better if you can get in\Nwhenever you need to, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.60,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,W—Wow, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.64,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Since exams are finally over,\Nwe can really get down to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.90,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.22,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're seriously talented, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.65,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You can produce this caliber\Nof drawing in just one day!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.41,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Those are no good at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.49,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.70,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The lines are too stiff.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.70,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The thickness and stress points are a mess.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.79,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,They couldn't pass as manga works.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.21,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.79,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's really hard to get used to the G-pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.17,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I just can't get the lines to\Nform the way I picture them.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.30,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I even tried using the Kabura pen once instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.38,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,A Kabura pen?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.18,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.68,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh. I thought fountain pens \Nreferred to that one in general.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.31,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Supposedly my uncle didn't know about G-pens\Neither. So he drew with a Kabura pen instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.43,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.52,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Then his editor told him to use a G-pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.35,0:06:23.44,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But he was used to the Kabura pen\Nand couldn't get the hang of the G-pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.69,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,So he ended up only using the Kabura pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.78,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You don't have much control\Nover the thickness of lines,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.58,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,but with a Kabura pen, it's much \Neasier to produce a consistent line.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.37,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,With a G-pen, on the other hand, you have \Nmuch more control over the intensity of lines.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.75,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But its inflexibility makes it \Nprone to get stuck on the paper.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.54,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.54,0:06:48.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,So the Kabura pen is no good, even \Nthough your uncle used one as a pro?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.09,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Of course it's no good!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.14,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,My pictures would have no dimension if I used it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.35,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,My uncle always insisted\Nthat his drawings were terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.06,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He said they just barely made the\Ncut because it was gag manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.52,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I guess he had a point—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.10,0:07:05.27,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's completely different from making sketches\Nin pencil, then filling it in with paint afterwards.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.74,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The only way is to practice till it hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.20,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Here's some more of the stuff I worked on last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.08,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Or I guess I shouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.58,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,He's not satisfied with this at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.25,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You can draw better backgrounds with a Kabura pen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.51,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,And a Maru pen can be used\Nfor the extremely thin lines.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Did you use those for a model?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.97,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I took out all of the stuff\Nthat was packed in those boxes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.85,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I didn't know they sold this sort of material—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.60,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You can make a great manuscript using this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.31,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Not without adding impact.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.44,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Impact?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.82,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,These.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.61,0:07:51.07,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Supposedly my uncle assigned these to his assistant using the numbers,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.95,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But we have to do it ourselves first.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.78,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're gonna draw all of these by hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Using these tools, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.46,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's not like we have an assistant,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.08,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,So we even have to apply\Nthe screen tones ourselves too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.63,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You cut these out with an art knife then apply them.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.51,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Basically, to make just one page\Nof a manuscript, we'd need to—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.13,0:08:17.47,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,First, we make a rough sketch on\Ndraft paper based on the name.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.93,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Then add in the characters and\Nthe background using a pen?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.93,0:08:25.19,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Right. Then we'd paint in the black,\Nimpact areas using a screen tone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,All that to finish just one page?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.36,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That's so much—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.24,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.78,0:08:36.37,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,That workflow process depends on\Nthe person, but that's basically it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.12,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I've finally realized just\Nhow much we have to master
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.21,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,before we can produce something worth submitting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.38,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's easy to draw a person standing still,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.09,0:08:52.55,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But unless I can capture movement,\Nexpressions, and create composition,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'll never become a pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.01,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,That'll take an incredible amount of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.01,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Thinking back on it now,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.01,0:09:04.19,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,it's amazing my uncle began as a complete\Namateur and debuted in just three years.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.15,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He didn't know about whiteout.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.15,0:09:11.11,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,So if he made even the slightest \Nmistake, he'd redraw the entire thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.19,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I—Is that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.74,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But we don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.95,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If we want an anime by the time we're eighteen,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.45,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,we don't have a second to waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.54,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko, I understand where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.21,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,But you should spend a little time\Nstudying the day before an exam.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.71,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.60,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I meant to study a little yesterday—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.55,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,but it was morning before I knew it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.97,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Before you knew it—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've got to start putting in effort now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.85,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,According to my uncle, that's one of the\Nconditions for becoming a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.02,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Conditions for becoming a mangaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.10,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,In the Kawaguchi Taro school of thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.77,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The three great conditions for becoming\Na mangaka, if you're not a genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.15,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,T—Teach me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.78,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:10:06.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2D393E&\fnBrianne's hand\pos(292.958,82.729)\blur1.003}{\fs52.646}Number One
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:10:06.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2D393E&\fnBrianne's hand\pos(292.958,141.392)\blur1.003}{\fs97.771}Pride
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.32,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Pride!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.41,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Think that you're way better than everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.03,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright, I've got that one down already.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,And on top of that, it's not\Njust pride. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.58,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,That would be called pride.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.92,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:13.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2D393E&\fnBrianne's hand\pos(292.958,82.729)\blur1.003}{\fs52.646}Number Two
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.58,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:13.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2D393E&\fnBrianne's hand\pos(292.958,141.392)\blur1.003}{\fs97.771}Effort
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.34,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, this time it's something \Nupstanding, Kawaguchi Taro-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.01,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,And lastly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:20.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H0D1213&\fnBrianne's hand\pos(256.901,138.383)\blur1.003}{\fs52.646}Number Three\N{\fs105.292}Luck
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.01,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yes, luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You serious? Luck?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.81,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.60,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,We're gamblers, not geniuses after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.90,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Just sitting around talking about our \Ndreams won't make them come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.86,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm gonna spend the entire weekend drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.20,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.03,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna read all of\Nthe manga in this studio!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.17,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,This "Father's Soul" story really gets to you—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.05,0:11:05.93,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,"My friends stood behind us in a row,\Nas if to watch till we were out of sight."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.60,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Thank you, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\c&H72736C&\fnGaramond\frz348.5\move(621.333,470.637,826,473.311,0,3527)\blur1.003}Modern\NJapanese
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.99,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Right, then next—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.15,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Suzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.27,Default,Suzuki,0,0,0,,Y—Yes sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.61,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.11,Default,Suzuki,0,0,0,,W—Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.11,0:11:17.15,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,No reason in particular.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.32,Default,Suzuki,0,0,0,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.57,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Ah Kawasaki, you read please.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.32,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're going to the studio after this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.41,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.24,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'll get this week's Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.41,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Who's on the cover for this week?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.71,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Do I need anything else?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.54,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.63,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Come here, come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.21,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.47,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Oh, the winner of the Tezuka Award's been announced.
