Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.55,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Look at the winner!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.64,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.68,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,His age! Look at how old he is!
