Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.28,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He's only fifteen—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.49,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He's only fifteen—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It says here he's still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.46,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Amazing scores from all the judges.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.21,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.00,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He kind of pisses me off.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.67,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.63,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Look at the 'A Word from the Author' section.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.63,0:12:23.59,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,"When everyone was off playing video\Ngames, I stayed in and worked hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.35,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'll continue to work hard in order to \Nbecome a bestseller in Jack one day."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.35,0:12:32.23,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Feels like he's insulting me\Nfor being one of those gamers.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.77,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We can surpass guys like this easily, don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.77,0:12:39.07,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,If you look closely, the only thing he's \Ngetting praised for is his planning ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.03,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,That's some confidence you've got there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.70,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,The rules are confidence,\Neffort, and luck, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.41,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,That's pride, effort, and luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.83,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Confidence sounds better, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.70,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ohh, Kochikame—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.58,Default-Italic,Saiko,0,0,0,,Winner of the Tezuka prize at fifteen—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.63,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Moritaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.34,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.84,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I know you're excited about getting the studio,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.93,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,but hanging out there every day is a little too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You have exams coming up, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.97,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.68,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.06,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,If so, then focus on your—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.23,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Could I have seconds please?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.85,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kayoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.61,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm going up to the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.78,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Wait up! I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Wow, that's great! So moe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.46,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,It's like you're a pro already!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.54,Default,Guy3,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.34,Default,Guy3,0,0,0,,If I got serious, I'd take the\Nwhole manga industry by storm.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.84,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, next I'll think up a story,\Nso will you draw the pictures?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.39,Default,Ishizawa,0,0,0,,I guess I could. But my rates are pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.93,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.93,Default,Ishizawa,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.89,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Why is everyone looking in the same direction?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.15,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,And you didn't draw past their shoulders.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Those guys were laughing, weren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.95,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,That was Takagi from class 2, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who was the other guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.70,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,Who was he again?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.12,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Miyoshi Kaya, Azuki's best friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.04,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.83,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Wait, I was asking about the guy who was drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.83,0:14:22.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ishizawa. Same grade as us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.01,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Does he wanna be a mangaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.01,0:14:29.80,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I wonder. It could just be a cry for attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.76,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I mean, if even Miyoshi could tell, his \Ndrawing skills won't get him very far.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.81,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Don't start slacking off just\Nbecause midterms are over!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.98,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,You still have your high school entrance exams.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.98,0:14:48.95,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Use these exams to think\Nseriously about your futures.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.49,Default,Students,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.70,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Right, time for class to start then.
