Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.71,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.59,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There are probably a decent number of people \Ntrying to become mangakas like us, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Probably, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.39,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Niizuma's only fifteen, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.10,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,There's Ishizawa too. But I\Ndon't know how serious he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.77,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I've decided: I'm fine just going to North Yakusa High.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,North Yakusa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.86,0:15:28.78,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It might be a fallback school for someone like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.24,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But for me, it's the lowest level that\Nmy parents still find acceptable.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.41,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I want as much time as I can get to draw manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.45,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're planning everything around\Nbecoming a mangaka, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.42,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I've never realized time was\Nsuch a precious resource.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.88,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I've never been this serious\Nabout anything before either!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.88,0:15:48.88,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You sure it's okay if you don't go to the same high school as Azuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.55,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I don't know where she's gonna go.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.18,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,She might end up at an all girl's school.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.43,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You could just ask her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.72,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,No. It's fine if we go to different schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's more—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.06,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,romantic that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.06,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.60,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,The DNA of an idealist—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fs37.437\bord0\c&H9886A1&\fnEPSON Pwwww\fax-0.3\frx5\fry0\frz-11\move(981.333,232.644,1038.667,231.307)\blur1.003}Graduation\NCeremony
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.52,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The next time we meet after middle school,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.90,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'll be a mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.82,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,And she'll be a voice actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fs37.437\bord0\b1\fnCorporate Rounded\c&HAFADB9&\pos(576.667,347.63)\fax0.06\frz18\blur1.003}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fs22.061\bord0\b1\fnCorporate Rounded\c&H828F9B&\frz17\fax0.06\pos(698,180.5)\blur1.003}Azuki Miho
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.87,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Until then, you'll just support\Neach other through texts!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.03,0:16:16.91,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.91,0:16:17.74,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.21,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Do you really want to copy your uncle that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.79,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,It's what {\i1}I{\i0} wanna do.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.29,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I think Azuki would like it this way too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.59,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.67,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You haven't even considered the possibility\Nthat Azuki will find another guy at her school?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.43,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.18,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I believe in Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.84,0:16:39.97,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're really going to North Yakusa, even\Nif it means being separated from Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.98,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Just to get more time to draw manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.98,0:16:43.73,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.90,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll go there too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.78,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.49,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,You should go to a good college prep school!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.24,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,If we're aiming to be mangakas together,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.24,0:16:59.45,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,then going to the same\Nschool is more convenient.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.66,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I don't want to waste time either.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.49,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,And also—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.88,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.02,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I originally thought I'd go to a good college,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.59,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,in case becoming a mangaka didn't work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.72,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,But I realized it's stupid to plan for failure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.97,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Shuujin—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,North Yakusa for me as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.72,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Don't you dare fail, Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.89,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I won't! I'll concentrate on my \Ndrawing now that I've decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.52,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I won't stand to be beaten\Nby kids our age anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.73,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.10,0:17:30.57,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I guess Niizuma Eiji is our first rival, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.04,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I guess Eiji already discussed with his editor,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.04,0:17:37.32,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,graduating high school and\Ngetting serialized simultaneously.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.24,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,He already has an editor?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.16,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm positive he does.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.54,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Once he gets that prize, it's like automatic.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.92,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If there's an editor who takes a liking to you, \Nyou can get paired up even without that prize.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.50,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,My uncle said so.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.46,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,An editor—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.84,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Eiji's getting farther and farther away from us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.30,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The quality and type of editor varies widely.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.26,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,So getting one at random is\Nnot always a great thing either.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.44,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Since the mangaka can't choose the editor himself,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.93,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,whether the editor is any good or not—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.81,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Depends on luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.27,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There are editors whose reputations are totally off.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.86,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There are editors who just come to\Npick up your work and do nothing else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.40,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There really are all types. You never know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.99,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.74,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Now for a sort of heartwarming editor story.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.28,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.58,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,There was an editor who told a novice manga \Nartist who'd been published elsewhere before,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.58,0:18:31.54,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,"I have good feelings about your work.\NWrite more and bring them here!"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.00,0:18:36.05,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But after he read about ten of them—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.05,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,He ran them through the shredder?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.22,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,How is this heartwarming at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.22,0:18:48.64,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,The novice was used to being turned \Ndown after they read the first couple pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.64,0:18:52.06,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,So he was really happy someone \Nread his work all the way to the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.15,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,In the pain and frustration\Nof having his work shredded,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.15,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,he joined a group of famous mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.28,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Sounds like a good story now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.82,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,And then, at his serialization meeting,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.79,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about doing that back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.21,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But I thought that you might grow, and \Nimprove even more if I {\i1}didn't{\i0} praise you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.21,0:19:11.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Th—Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.80,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound true.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.05,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Supposedly that editor\Nbecame editor-in-chief after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.30,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Sounds like a manga story.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.26,0:19:28.18,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,My uncle said most editors are like \Nthat, really passionate about manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.94,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,He said they're all people who just love manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.31,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.31,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.82,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Wanna go see an editor?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.57,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,If we called and said we had something to\Nshow them, we could probably meet one.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.16,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,We probably could, but we \Ndon't have anything to show yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.79,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Let's finish something over summer break!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.54,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Then bring it to Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.25,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Jack's the best option since we\Nwant an anime and serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.13,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work out, we don't lose anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.34,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Let's find out what an editor\Nwould think of our work.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.39,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Let's see if our combined\Ntalents can get through to them!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.02,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.35,0:20:16.27,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Let's finish a work over summer\N break and bring it to Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.27,0:20:16.98,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.99,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Now that's out of the way, let's get to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.65,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.66,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, look—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.33,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Azuki—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:38.71,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I knew she had a younger sister \Nbut I didn't know she was this cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.76,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Oh man, what do I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.22,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to freeze up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.68,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's your chance to ask for her email!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.10,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,But her lioness of a mother is here too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.10,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah, she'd be dangerous one-on-one.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.81,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.64,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Let's just pretend we didn't \Nnotice them and not say anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.44,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.31,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's kind of obvious we {\i1}did{\i0} notice—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.27,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,Just go!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.07,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Looks like she's noticed us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.95,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,She's clearly blushing too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.36,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,And hiding behind her mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.45,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,No one asked for live commentary!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Miho, aren't those your classmates?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.68,Default,Sister,0,0,0,,Your face is all red, sis!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.43,Default,Azuki,0,0,0,,Mina!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.14,0:21:30.10,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Both of you are so shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you can pretend not to \Nknow each other when you're in the same class.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.56,Default,Saiko,0,0,0,,I said shut up!
